    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>Your spirit is so dense it takes on tangible force. Make a melee Strike with your weapon ikon. This counts as two attacks when calculating your multiple attack penalty. If this Strike hits, your additional spirit damage increases to 4 plus an extra die of weapon damage. If you're at least 10th level, increase this to 6 spirit damage and two extra dice, and if you're at least 18th level, increase it to 8 spirit damage and three extra dice. Constructs and objects are not immune to spirit damage dealt by this attack, and this spirit damage automatically bypasses any Hardness they have.</p>"
